{% call components.section("Overview") -%}
<p>A Video thumbnail is a graphical preview of a video overlayed with a play button. When it’s selected, a video player modal will be displayed so a user can watch the video at a larger size.</p>
{%- endcall %}

{% call components.section("Sample component") -%}
  <img src="{{ '/assets/video-thumbnail/video-thumbnail.svg' | url }}" alt="Video thumbnail" style="--inline-img-max-width: 555px;">
{%- endcall %}

{%- componentStatus -%}{% endcomponentStatus %}

{% call components.section("Style") -%}
  <p>A video thumbnail is a combination of a graphic with a slightly transparent play button on top. A video thumbnail can also include an optional caption underneath that explains what the video is.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='light') %}
